**Proprietary client protocols**

**[Microsoft](/Microsoft)** mail systems use the **[proprietary](/Proprietary_software)** **[Messaging Application Programming Interface](/Messaging_Application_Programming_Interface)** (MAPI) in client applications, such as **[Microsoft Outlook](/Microsoft_Outlook)**, to access **[Microsoft Exchange](/Microsoft_Exchange_Server)** electronic mail servers.

